e value before asking for full notification access:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["func application(_ application: UIApplication,","                didFinishLaunchingWithOptions launchOptions: [UIApplication.LaunchOptionsKey: Any]?) -> Bool {","","    if #available(iOS 12.0, *) {","        Pushwoosh.configure.setAdditionalAuthorizationOptions([.provisional])","    }","","    Pushwoosh.configure.registerForPushNotifications()","","    return true","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"text":"In-App Notification Settings","type":"heading","anchor":"In-App-Notification-Settings","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Add a “Configure in App” button to the system Settings > Notifications screen for your app. When the user taps it, implement the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"openSettingsFor"},{"type":"text","text":" callback to navigate to your custom settings screen:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["func application(_ application: UIApplication,","                didFinishLaunchingWithOptions launchOptions: [UIApplication.LaunchOptionsKey: Any]?) -> Bool {","","    if #available(iOS 12.0, *) {","        Pushwoosh.configure.setAdditionalAuthorizationOptions([.providesAppNotificationSettings])","    }","","    Pushwoosh.configure.addNotificationCenterDelegate(self)","    Pushwoosh.configure.registerForPushNotifications()","","    return true","}","","\/\/ Called when user taps \"Configure in App\" in system notification settings","func userNotificationCenter(_ center: UNUserNotificationCenter,","                            openSettingsFor notification: UNNotification?) {","    \/\/ Navigate to your in-app notification settings screen","}"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Critical Alerts","level":2,"anchor":"Critical-Alerts"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For medical, health, and safety apps that need to bypass Do Not Disturb and the mute switch. Requires a special entitlement approved by Apple:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["if #available(iOS 12.0, *) {","    Pushwoosh.configure.setAdditionalAuthorizationOptions([.criticalAlert])","}","","Pushwoosh.configure.registerForPushNotifications()"],"type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Combining Multiple Options","anchor":"Combining-Multiple-Options","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Options can be combined:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["if #available(iOS 12.0, *) {","    Pushwoosh.configure.setAdditionalAuthorizationOptions([.provisional, .providesAppNotificationSettings])","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Objective-C:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"objc","code":["if (@available(iOS 12.0, *)) {","    [Pushwoosh.configure setAdditionalAuthorizationOptions:UNAuthorizationOptionProvisional | UNAuthorizationOptionProvidesAppNotificationSettings];","}","","[Pushwoosh.configure registerForPushNotifications];"]}]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS/documentation/PushwooshFramework/Pushwoosh/additionalAuthorizationOptions":{"abstract":[{"text":"Additional notification authorization options beyond the SDK defaults.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshframework\/pushwoosh\/additionalauthorizationoptions","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"additionalAuthorizationOptions","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@E@UNAuthorizationOptions","text":"UNAuthorizationOptions","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"type":"topic","title":"additionalAuthorizationOptions","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"additionalAuthorizationOptions","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/Pushwoosh\/additionalAuthorizationOptions"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS/documentation/PushwooshFramework":{"title":"PushwooshFramework","kind":"s